      <title>心若雏子, 则灵台自清</title>
      <link>https://gitaeron.github.io/cn/moment/%E6%96%87%E8%A8%80%E6%96%87%E8%A8%80%E6%84%9F/2023-02-27-%E5%BF%83%E8%8B%A5%E5%A4%84%E5%AD%90%E5%88%99%E7%81%B5%E5%8F%B0%E8%87%AA%E6%B8%85/</link>
